[normal]Confidence in the CLG Committee has now been completely undermined by its having allowed the LGO to hijack the agenda yet again – this time by setting up its own friendly pseudo-independent investigation. The effect of this is to bolster the LGO’s privileg
[normal]ed position as a firmly-entrenched master of whitewashing both its own and also local authorities’ maladministration with impunity, and 
[normal]of 
[normal]manipulating 
[normal]complacent 
